function Start()
	idAsaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_AsaStart)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAsaClone, actor_AsaEnd, "NPC_Walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idAsaClone, actor_AsaEnd)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idAsaClone, 0, actor_AsaEnd)
	end
end
